-- Russia Bans Alcohol for Olympic Delegation, Kommersant Reports
-- B y   M a r i n a   S y s o y e v a
-- 2012-05-21T04:15:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-21/russia-bans-alcohol-for-olympic-delegation-kommersant-reports.html
Russia  has banned consumption of
alcohol by members of the country’s delegation at the London
Olympic games,  Kommersant  reported, citing the protocol of a
government meeting.  Alcoholic drinks won’t be offered at any events organized
by the Russian delegation from July 27 to Aug. 12, the newspaper
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Marina Sysoyeva in Moscow at 
 msysoyeva@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
